==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underestimate
<hw>Un`der*es"ti*mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To set
too low a value on; to estimate below the truth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underestimate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Underestimate
<hw>Un`der*es"ti*mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
underestimating; too low an estimate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underfaction</ent>⟦br⟧
